{"tid":1550481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"明天美國領事館，如有人掉氣油彈，點搞條友？","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:34:24.000Z","uid":305755,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"52ead56959751070313957e8e5f9ac4c459e65e9","tid":1550481,"uid":305755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d8426314deb8d5ef7bcea2f76971750d90b50fd6","tid":1550481,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c4dd2444dc5b771c2063121b59b7c8157afa607","tid":1550481,"uid":305755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8bdd6dd1037361772041b5ce20716c9b292a8c31","tid":1550481,"uid":263219,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"制服交比美國大使館保安"},{"pid":"eb235a7b595959952ca17ee204b02e3d49ecf1b9","tid":1550481,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"睇下掉邊，掉入美領就影大頭"},{"pid":"d86454d5bae157ed60705f44fdb519e6553c678f","tid":1550481,"uid"